snippet.title: Memories of East Coast — Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Launch Trailer —  Visual Novel | Memories of East Coast
A debut game of an immersive visual novel experience that brings you on a journey through memory, nostalgia and guilt. Will you accept your fate?

Available on:
(itch.io) https://roomahgaming.itch.io/moec
(Steam) https://store.steampowered.com/app/1607430/Memories_of_East_Coast/
(PS4 | PS5) https://store.playstation.com/en-sg/concept/10003807
(Nintendo Switch) https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/memories-of-east-coast-switch/

Music playlist — https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLiaz62ACps7T68jMzyYIfBFfND_5cqHBB
